, as we can choose a subsequence if we have to.
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $R^{c}([p_{n}])\subseteq\{D\geq n\}$
\end_inset

, we have that
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
1-\alpha\leq\int_{R^{c}([p_{n}])}p_{n}d\mu\leq\int_{D\geq n}p_{n}d\mu\label{eq:inequality with R^c}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

for all 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

.
 By Lemma 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
