noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, we get
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{D=\infty}p^{\star}d\mu\geq1-\alpha>0.
\]

\end_inset

Let 
\begin_inset Formula $P\in\mathcal{P}$
\end_inset

 be arbitrary, 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 be its density, and consider
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P(D=\infty)=\int_{D=\infty}\left(\frac{p}{p^{\star}}\right)p^{\star}d\mu.
\]

\end_inset

Since 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{D=\infty}p^{\star}d\mu>0$
\end_inset

